\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.7}{\ignorespaces Conflict resolution comparison. In v4 (left), both facts score near equally ($\Delta = 0.028 < 0.30$) and both reach the LLM, causing a hedged answer. In v5 (right), temporal decay widens the gap to $1.126 \gg 0.30$; the stale 2010 fact is discarded before the LLM is called, yielding a correct answer.}}{41}{figure.caption.44}%
